<section id="bio" class="bio">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Hello</p>
    <h2>One person, many surfaces.</h2>
    <div class="bio-body">
      <p>
        I'm a Gen X founder-operator and writer. Twenty-five years inside Microsoft and Amazon, then displaced by ageism and the same wave of AI I now happen to be very good with. I rebuilt as a one-person company running a portfolio of media and publishing projects with Claude as my integrated executive partner, and the work I'm doing now is the most generative run of my life&mdash;a sentence I did not expect to write at fifty-six.
      </p>
      <p>
        What you'll find here: writing on hinge moments in politics, technology, and culture; near-future scenarios; a novel-in-progress called <em>The Shattered World Series</em>; and the projects I've built or co-built along the way. Kintsugi as method, defiant joy as resistance, a small group changing the course of history.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

